Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.70,0:00:44.89,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Love，I've got to feel it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.03,0:00:48.16,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}If you put your trust in me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.32,0:00:51.55,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I know what my life would be
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.65,0:00:56.60,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Oh，you are all I ever need
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:01:02.19,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I try to hear what you say
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.30,0:01:04.43,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}So I pray
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.44,0:01:08.22,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}But you're fading away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:15.45,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Don't go and break my fragile heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.67,0:01:18.93,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}We won't fall apart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.93,0:01:26.86,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}'Cause you're my only star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:32.62,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I wonder why my tears come at night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.66,0:01:36.15,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Calling you，so like a little child
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.30,0:01:39.57,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}All the things you have in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.68,0:01:42.71,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I wish I could see your insides
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.82,0:01:45.78,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}My love，you've got to feel it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.78,0:01:49.27,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}And if we put our trust in you and me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.28,0:01:52.74,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}You know what our lives would be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:02:00.15,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)}Oh，you are the one I believe
