Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:56.84,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}微微  清风徐来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:21:04.14,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}飒飒  漫逐云端
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.51,0:21:11.28,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}音色交织  光灿闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.49,0:21:14.79,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}纵是凋落的希望
